% =============================================================================
%  literature.bib — consolidated bibliography for the MIPT FPMI master's
%  entrance-exam preparation repo.
%
%  Source of truth: программа.pdf and the per-section README.md files under
%  core/ and electives/. One BibTeX entry per recommended title.
%
%  Conventions
%  -----------
%    * Citation keys are ASCII-only (BibTeX-portable) and tagged by section:
%        ru:<Author><Year>     for Russian-language sources cited in section X
%        en:<Author><Year>     for English-language sources
%      A trailing letter (a, b, …) disambiguates same-author/same-year items.
%    * Original Russian titles are preserved (UTF-8). For BibTeX engines that
%      do not handle UTF-8, switch to biblatex + biber, or transliterate.
%    * `keywords` field lists the program section(s) that cite the work,
%      so you can pull a per-section subset with e.g.
%          \nocite{*} + \printbibliography[keyword=core-1.1]
%
%  Sections
%  --------
%    Core 1.1  Calculus and linear algebra
%    Core 1.2  Probability theory, statistics, stochastic processes
%    Core 1.3  Algorithms and data structures
%    Core 1.4  Introduction to AI
%    2.1       Equations of mathematical physics & numerical methods
%    2.2       Discrete analysis & higher algebra
%    2.3a      Logic & theoretical CS
%    2.3b      Programming fundamentals
%    2.4       Convex analysis, optimization, optimal control
%    2.5       Advanced AI methods
%    2.6       IT product management
% =============================================================================


